{"tid":2434224,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"國務卿布林肯：反對再以軍事干預行動去促進民主！","createTime":"2021-03-05T11:18:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-05T11:38:59.000Z","uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"fc6fbf0335d3b4cb0321bf0fa8fe35bb76e9bf1a","tid":2434224,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T11:18:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/www.881903.com/news/amp/international/2381452\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fs%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Famp%2Finternational%2F2381452&d=sOSR1epLEapJbLCvIyWedf8K46P7%2BXxs1F7ZCKkfkQw%3D&h=7bad82d4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/www.881903.com/news/amp/international/2381452</a><br />\n<br />\n美國國務卿布林肯在國務院發表外交政策演說，表明不贊成美國再以代價高昂的軍事干預行動去促進民主，指美國過往曾以這種策略或透過武力去試圖推翻獨裁政權，雖然意願良好，但不奏效，而且破壞促進民主的名聲，令美國人民失去信心。美國未來會採取不同的處理方式。<br />\n<br />\n布林肯說，雖然美國的民主脆弱，但認為袛有美國可以團結其他國家，解決自身無法解決的問題，又指美國在國際舞台上缺席，將導致混亂及出現另類領導層，損害美國的利益及價值觀。"},{"pid":"0e8e8a14d8826e73b5c518f7057af607fa0b2776","tid":2434224,"uid":114193,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T11:21:15.000Z","msg":"［新任務］要學識唔能夠再俾新聞影響到自己情緒！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2432822\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2432822</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n雖然連下sir 今日已經share 左6-7篇新聞<br />\n不過大家都唔好俾新聞影響情緒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e96f034e970308a1ae25dbead9a15b5dc31ee1a","tid":2434224,"uid":235152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T11:38:59.000Z","msg":"全世界等你救,你就解甲走人韓戰越戰伊拉克次次打打下唔打或走人先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}